      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and features the factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its communicative feedback with refreshed bushings, while the braking system provides consistent bite with minimal fade. Though it displays the honest patina of a well-enjoyed driver, the mechanical synchronization and linear power delivery remain superlative. A robust, road-ready icon for the purist.",
